Robyn Ludwick - Out Of These Blues (2011)

Out of These Blues is the third album of Texas Country/Blues artist Robyn Ludwick
released February 7 2011, the album received Top 10 Albums of 2011 honors from
Austin City Limits, No Depression, Texas Music Magazine and 93.3 KGSR as well as
Best Album of 2011 by the Texas Music Scene.
